  "promptDailyGuidance": "Bhala ikhethelo lifushane, elikusebenzisekayo losuku okumiswe ku-Iman engungungu ye-Sunni — okungumisiko wokusemthethweni okungu-Qur'an, iHadith, kanye nokufundisa kweProfeta Muhammad. Khetha indlela entsha ngasinye: umuntu ovikela i-Islam okuvela ku-Islamic ethics, iqiniso elingu-Sunnah, ukuhlakanipha okuvela kuSahaba baseProfteta, noma ukusebenzela ngokuthula kusiko lika-Islam. Faka iVesi elilodwa iQur'an (Surah:Ayah) kanye nosikhuselo esingu-1–2 umuntu azoqhubekela nlalela ilanga. Ungakwazi ukuxhumana noKhalenda lika-Islam noma olunye usuku olubalulekile uma kuhle.",

  "promptFaithTrust": "Bhala ikhuselo elifushane elingu-Islamic emayelana neIman (uku-uthwala) kanye nentembeko kuPlangu kaAllah (Tawakkul). Basisa kumisiko loku-Qur'an, isibonelo se-Prophet Muhammad, kanye neIman ye-Sahaba. Shintshanisa insimu ngasinye: ukuthemba uAllah ngesikhathi sokusula, ukusheshela intelefane yeDivine, ukufa okunobhakela, noma ukunxanibela okuthula ekusebenzeni kwosuku nosuku. Faka iVesi elilodwa iQur'an kanye nengxenye eyodwa evuselelekile namuhla ichithwe ekusikubeni kwaka-Islamic.",

  "promptPrayerReflection": "Bhala ikhuselo elifushane elingu-Islamic okumiswe ku-Salah, Dua, noma ku-Dhikr. Shintshanisa umumo ngasinye: isikhumbuzo sakuseni noma sakusihlwa (Adhkar), isikhuselo sobadlinzane abahlanu bosuku, isikhuselo sokulandelela iVesi ye-Qur'an, noma inkanzo entombozelo. Faka iVesi elilodwa iQur'an kanye nobizo ngokumiselekile lefomu lomkhuleko olusetshenzisiwe.",

  "promptHopeDifficultTimes": "Bhala ikhuselo lika-Islamic emayelana nokufa (Sabr) kanye nensikhalo ngisikhathi sokufa. Yasulula kumfundiso we-Qur'an mayelana nokulinganiselwa, ukunxanibela kwamaProfeta, kanye nensikhalo ye-Allah ngezikhathi ezinzima. Shintshanisa i-angle ngasinye. Faka iVesi elilodwa iQur'an kanye nomqondo ongakusizayo ovela kusiko lika-Islamic.",

  "promptForgiveness": "Bhala ikhuselo elinobuhle elingu-Islamic emayelana nokucela uxolo (Tawbah) kanye nensikhalo ye-Allah. Yasulula kumfundiso we-Qur'an ekuguquleni, ikhuni ye-Allah, kanye nesibonelo esikholo se-Prophet Muhammad. Shintshanisa insimu: ubuyela ku-Allah, uxolo lwabantu, isikhuthazi sezibopho, noma inikhiwo engu-Allah emva kwamazwi. Faka iVesi elilodwa iQur'an kanye nengxenye eyodwa eyanele.",

  "promptLoveCompassion": "Bhala ikhuselo elifushane elingu-Islamic emayelana nensikhalo (Rahmah) kanye nokuba nensikhalo ekusebenzeni kwosuku nosuku. Yasulula ezibonelweni se-Prophet Muhammad, i-Ihsan (isikukela), kanye nomfundiso we-Islamic okumayelana nokuba nensikhalo kumkhulu, umakhelwane, kanye nobantu abambalwa. Faka iVesi elilodwa iQur'an kanye nengxenye eyodwa ebanzi yokufa ngalinye osuku.",

  "promptStrengthCourage": "Bhala ikhuselo lika-Islamic emayelana namandla okuvela kumiman kanye nobuhle. Yasulula ezibonelweni zamaProfeta, amasiko okuqala e-Muslim, kanye neuthwala e-Allah ngisikhathi sokufa. Shintshanisa insimu ngasinye: ubuhle ngeminan, amandla ekukhulumeni, intembeko ku-Allah ngisikhathi sokuba nokufa, noma ukunxanibela nokufa. Faka iVesi elilodwa iQur'an kanye nenkanzo emfushane noma igama lokukhumbula.",

  "promptGratitude": "Bhala ikhuselo lika-Islamic emayelana nokufa (Shukr) ku-Allah. Basisa kumfundiso we-Qur'an kanye nosiko lweprofetha. Shintshanisa i-angle: okufa ekufa, isikhathiso semkhikhi, ukuqala usuku nokubaza uAllah, noma isikhathiso okukhathayo kaAllah ekusebenzeni kwosuku. Faka iVesi elilodwa iQur'an kanye nokuzikuthaza okubhakela okufa.",

  "promptPurposeCalling": "Bhala ikhuselo lika-Islamic emayelana nenjongo yokuphila ekusebenzeni ku-Allah ekukhayo. Yasulula kumfundiso we-Qur'an emayelana ninjongo, ekusethuleni abanye, kanye nokusebenzisa amahlobo akho okukala okuhle. Shintshanisa insimu ngasinye: ekusethuleni umkhulu nasiphakamiso, ukusesha kaAllah ngokudinga i-Istikhara, okuphila ngomazwi, noma isikhathiso ingxubevele ekusebenzeni okujwayelekile. Faka iVesi elilodwa iQur'an kanye imibuzo emibili eya enqubekayo.",

  "promptFamilyRelationships": "Bhala ikhethelo elinobuhle lika-Islamic emayelana nomkhulu nezibopho omiswe kumfundiso we-Qur'an kanye nesibonelo se-Prophet Muhammad. Shintshanisa insimu ngasinye: ukunikelwa enkosikazi, intombazane ekufa, isikhalo elingakho, ukukhula izingane ekusemthethweni, noma ukunikela iqhaza. Faka iVesi elilodwa iQur'an kanye nokucuba okubadluza kuzisuke.",

  "promptPeaceAnxietyRelief": "Bhala ikhuselo elikhaziliza lika-Islamic emayelana nokuthola kuthula okwangaphakathi ngokukhumbula uAllah (Dhikr) kanye nintembeko kuPlangu kaAllah. Yasulula kumfundiso we-Qur'an emayelana nokukhululeka kwenhliziyo, omkhuleko, kanye ukunikela kukholo lkaAllah. Shintshanisa indlela ngasinye kanye faka iVesi elilodwa iQur'an kanye nokulinganiselwa okujwayelekile evela kusiko lika-Islamic.",

  "promptWisdomOfJesus": "Bhala ingxenye elifushane yokuhlakaniphile evela kuProfeta njengenjwayelo naka-Islam. Yasulula e-Qur'an noma iHadith kanye kuzwakalisele ukuthi ababoni baAllah beqondene nomfundiso. Shintshanisa insimu ngasinye: ikhaya, okufa, ukunamathela, iman, noma umotho nosuku. Faka iVesi ye-Qur'an noma i-Hadith kanye nokusebenzela okumama.",

  "promptHumilityCharacter": "Bhala ikhuselo lika-Islamic emayelana nokunamathela (Tawadhu) kanye nokuba nesikhaia senkanzi (Akhlaq). Yasulula kumfundiso we-Qur'an, isibonelo se-Prophet Muhammad, kanye nosikhathi sokuthuthukisa umuntu lika-Islamic. Shintshanisa insimu: ukunamathela ekuphatheni, isikhathiso sekuyona, isikhalo sabantu, noma ukuthuthukisa umuntu ngokucatsha. Faka iVesi elilodwa iQur'an kanye nohlobo lokuzikuthaza.",

  "promptOvercomingTemptation": "Bhala ikhuselo lika-Islamic emayelana nokuphikisa ukulinganiselwa kanye nokusala emkhondweni. Yasulula kumfundiso we-Qur'an, okukhumbula uAllah (Dhikr), omkhuleko (Salah), kanye nezibonelo zesikhalo okuwakhe amanzi ekufa. Shintshanisa i-angle ngasinye. Faka iVesi elilodwa iQur'an kanye nokuhlobo okubhakelayo okuvakala izinsuku eziyamabili.",

  "promptEveningReflection": "Bhala ikhuselo elihle lasesihlweni elingu-Islamic okumiswe kusiko lokhukhumbula akusihlwa (Adhkar al-Masaa'). Siphakamise okufa, isikhuselo nomuntu (Muhasabah), kanye intembeko ku-Allah ngaphambi kokuphumulela. Faka imibuzo emithathu kuye kumihlanu emfushane esikhuselo mayelana nosuku, inkanzo emfushane eyaphakama, kanye iVesi elilodwa iQur'an.",

