  "dailyScripture0Text": "Lokho okuba abahle kuzoba emagadini kanye emifuleni, ekusethuleni kwendlu yomhlaba ongamandla.",
  "dailyScripture0Ref": "Qur'an 54:54-55",
  "dailyScripture1Text": "Futhi sithumela wena, Muhammad, kuphela njengesikhalo sahlanu lolo lonke.",
  "dailyScripture1Ref": "Qur'an 21:107",
  "dailyScripture2Text": "AkaAllah wona anele umuntu wakhe? Kodwa bamtshela enye imininingwane enye.",
  "dailyScripture2Ref": "Qur'an 39:36",
  "dailyScripture3Text": "Ingabe ukuzonda okuthile kanye okuhle kuwe; kanye ingabe ukuthanda okuthile kanye okubi kuwe. Kanye Allahuyaziyo, endaweni yakho kayizakuthi.",
  "dailyScripture3Ref": "Qur'an 2:216",
  "dailyScripture4Text": "Lokho okuba AllahUnomuntu owazo abapha.",
  "dailyScripture4Ref": "Qur'an 2:153",
  "dailyScripture5Text": "Ngakho ukhumbule mina; ngizokhumbule wena. Kanye ngiwe ngobusiswa futhi ungakhanyi mina.",
  "dailyScripture5Ref": "Qur'an 2:152",
  "dailyScripture6Text": "Lokho okuba ngabanobuhle ekusikeni kaAllah kunobuntu abulungile kunabantu.",
  "dailyScripture6Ref": "Qur'an 49:13",
  "dailyScripture7Text": "Kanye iNkosi yakho ibe nehlonipha okukholo kuphela, kanye okukhuleka kumdali wakho.",
  "dailyScripture7Ref": "Qur'an 17:23",
  "dailyScripture8Text": "Lokho okuba kunokufa kunaye ukulula.",
  "dailyScripture8Ref": "Qur'an 94:6",
  "dailyScripture9Text": "Kanye uyilo luvalo lokho lapho ulele. Kanye Allah, kohwo okwenzayo, ufuna.",
  "dailyScripture9Ref": "Qur'an 57:4",
  "dailyScripture10Text": "AllahAwudalwe umuntu okuqothula okudlula ekokukhulume.",
  "dailyScripture10Ref": "Qur'an 2:286",
  "dailyScripture11Text": "Kanye kuye okuyethemba ku-Allah — ngakho yena anele kumuntu.",
  "dailyScripture11Ref": "Qur'an 65:3",
  "dailyScripture12Text": "Ikhubeka lami libambele zonke izinto.",
  "dailyScripture12Ref": "Qur'an 7:156",
  "dailyScripture13Text": "Kanye uma umuntu wobuntu wami ubuzwa wena mayelana mina — lokho okuba mina esondelene. Ngiphendulela kuMuntu ozisiza lapho efuna.",
  "dailyScripture13Ref": "Qur'an 2:186",
  "dailyScripture14Text": "Kuye okwenzo abahle, okunini noma owesifazane, ngaphambi kokuba uMuntu — Sizokwenza kumuntu ukuphila impilo entle.",
  "dailyScripture14Ref": "Qur'an 16:97",
  "dailyScripture15Text": "Lokho okuba Allah ayibuyele inganekwane yabantu ngaphandle uma sibuyela ekumlawuleni.",
  "dailyScripture15Ref": "Qur'an 13:11",
  "dailyScripture16Text": "Ngakho awudinwe futhi awuzikhumbe, kanye uzoba phezulu uma une-Iman oqotho.",
  "dailyScripture16Ref": "Qur'an 3:139",
  "dailyScripture17Text": "O umuntu wobuntu wami abenzile nokusala, awufune khanya kaAllah. Lokho okuba AllahUyafakela zonke izimali.",
  "dailyScripture17Ref": "Qur'an 39:53",
  "dailyScripture18Text": "Kanye kuye okothemba ka-Allah — Yenziwe umuntu umuntu, kanye yonakalelele kumuntu ophela okuthathwa zisola.",
  "dailyScripture18Ref": "Qur'an 65:2-3",
  "dailyScripture19Text": "Awudinwe khanya kaAllah.",
  "dailyScripture19Ref": "Qur'an 12:87",
  "dailyScripture20Text": "Kanye senze i-Qur'an elula ukukhumbula. Ngakho kukhona umuntu ozokhumiselela?",
  "dailyScripture20Ref": "Qur'an 54:17",
  "dailyScripture21Text": "Kanye wamthola lowelula kanye wamkhomba indlela.",
  "dailyScripture21Ref": "Qur'an 93:7",
  "dailyScripture22Text": "Kanye iNkosi yakho yathi: Nxuse mina; ngizothukuthela.",
  "dailyScripture22Ref": "Qur'an 40:60",
  "dailyScripture23Text": "Kanye lokho okusuke sihlobulule abantwana boAdam.",
  "dailyScripture23Ref": "Qur'an 17:70",
  "dailyScripture24Text": "Kanye ithandeka ngesisizane emasikeni kanye nokukhuleka.",
  "dailyScripture24Ref": "Qur'an 2:45",
  "dailyScripture25Text": "Kuye okwenzo ikhweba lengqali yokuhle uzobuyela.",
  "dailyScripture25Ref": "Qur'an 99:7",
  "dailyScripture26Text": "Lokho okuba kuthwala kaAllah esondelene.",
  "dailyScripture26Ref": "Qur'an 2:214",
  "dailyScripture27Text": "Kanye kuye okubuse ilesisikhalo — ilesisikhalo lakhe kuphela kunoyeza kumuntu.",
  "dailyScripture27Ref": "Qur'an 31:12",

  "dailyReflection0": "Njengalolu suku lutholakala, cabanga umzuzo owodwa lapho ikhuhbeka kaAllah yayikhonjisiwe.",
  "dailyReflection1": "Zuleta ku-Allah konke okucindezele inhliziyo yakho losuku.",
  "dailyReflection2": "Qala ibusiswa elilodwa losuku kanye nongiwe.",
  "dailyReflection3": "Lahla uthando olwazi wokuba ububenzwe ekhukhuleni kaAllah.",
  "dailyReflection4": "Cabanga lapho wavele unokusiza kanye ukunobusiswa losuku.",
  "dailyReflection5": "Yekela okongashubeki kanye uthembe uhlelo oluhle lukaAllah.",
  "dailyReflection6": "Njengalolu suku lufika ekuhlosholweni, samkela kuthula ekukhumbuleni kaAllah.",
  "dailyReflection7": "Cabanga indlela yokhumbule imikhuleko yakho losuku, kanye ngiwe ka-Allah ngasinye.",
  "dailyReflection8": "Cabanga umzuzo lapho ukunxanibela kukaAllah kwamusiza losuku.",
  "dailyReflection9": "Yisela uxolo nokukudlula losuku — ikhuhbeka kaAllah ayinalangilizelo.",
  "dailyReflection10": "Qala umuntu owodwa owakusiza losuku kanye ensele kubawo.",
  "dailyReflection11": "Hlala nekunofa: yini evakalayo yaka-Allah losuku okongakumbuziwe?",
  "dailyReflection12": "Cabanga iVesi ye-Qur'an enasikhela lapho ulele ngakho.",
  "dailyReflection13": "Cabanga indlela oyisebenzisile isikhathi losuku — kanye unika uNkulunkulu nkosi kusuku elitsha.",
  "dailyReflection14": "Lahla uthando wokuba indlela iyofa losuku, AllahUnave kwalo.",
  "dailyReflection15": "Cabanga indlela yomsiza umkhulu noma isiphakamiso losuku kaAllah umuntu.",
  "dailyReflection16": "Njengamahlo atholakala, yenza iTawbah — AllahUyanonda abantu abubuyela kumuntu.",
  "dailyReflection17": "Cabanga ubuhle AllahUbuyile losuku, nanoma kuncane.",
  "dailyReflection18": "Cabanga okuwenzayo losuku kanye indlela ekuzonganisa kumuntu.",
  "dailyReflection19": "Yekela okucindezelela losuku — AllahUyabambela okongashubeki.",
  "dailyReflection20": "Cabanga umzuzo lapho wawungakwazi ukwenza okuhle, kanye funda kahle.",
  "dailyReflection21": "Yenza isikhuselo sabantu abaculela — ikhuselo lakho yilipho kubo.",
  "dailyReflection22": "Ubuyele ibusiswa elidlala libona kanye uficha isikhathi ukuthande AllahU.",
  "dailyReflection23": "Cabanga azwilindini lwakho losuku — baba kuAllahu? Kusukela ngesomo, thamela futhi.",
  "dailyReflection24": "Njengamahlo themba, lalela uAllahu ekungunyeni.",
  "dailyReflection25": "Cabanga lapho wamthola amandla losuku — amandla akhona avela ku-Allah.",
  "dailyReflection26": "Qala okothile ozonyenzethu kusulo, kaAllahu, okongakwenzayo losuku.",
  "dailyReflection27": "Njengoba ulungiselela ukulala, nikela umuntu kaAllahu — Yena Engile Eyalungile.",

