  "disclaimerTitle": "Mayelana nekhethelo lesi-app",
  "disclaimerBody": "U-Ayara unikeza izikhuselo ze-Islamic, izikhumbulo, kanye okusesikholo okusizakala ekuhambi kwakho kweiman. Lokhu okusesikholo kunikeza ngenhloso yokuziwa nokunethezeka kuphela.\n\nU-Ayara awubuyeli ulwazi oluzinhlobonhlobo.\nIkhethelo ku-app lolu ayisimonakelo somlizali osesichazamthethweni, imam, mufti, noma umfundisi obambe ikhaya. Uma une-imibuzo mayelana nokutshela kwabantu kaAllah, halal noma haram, noma okudingelwa umuntu, ngubani umlizali onesichazamthethweni owesichazamthethweni esikhalweni sakho.\n\nI-app lolu ayifakeli olwazi olunokushona.\nU-Ayara ayenza okushona olunokushona mayelana nokubudonda (Islamic jurisprudence) noma okudingelwa umuntu. Lokho laphakathi ayingumuntu owanele kumuntu noma okudingelwa umlizali.\n\nUkuhlakanipha kwesichazamthethweni kunokuhlobuka.\nI-Islam iqukethe ubuhle obuningi bokwethulela, izikole zokucabanga (madhabs), kanye nomqondo wesichazamthethweni. Okusesikholo ku-app lekunabububezi kumuntu beneral kanye awungamele isikole noma isiko ngasinye.\n\nAmasiko ayabalulekile.\nI-app lolu ifuna ukuthuthukisa inkuleka yakho sezikole okusesikholo ngokuze uhonore umlumelwano wemosikwini wakho, imam, kanye nesikhole samasiko. Siyakubangela wena uhlale naye kanye ufunde ezintsha umlizali oselengu-qualified kusikole lakho.",
  "disclaimerClose": "Ngiyaqonda",
  "disclaimerInfoTooltip": "Mayelana nekhethelo lesi-app",
  "disclaimerSettingsSubtitle": "Kumayelana nokuziwa kuphela. Thinta ukuze ufunde ichibi lonke.",
  "disclaimerSectionHeader": "Ichibi lekhethelo"
}